#: ../../testting.rst:5 c583a11ef07c44b0825fe2de2cd1a9e6
msgid "单元测试"
msgstr "Testting"

#: ../../testting.rst:7 0821d1e1ce6b480e9924baa4ee6a5cb2
msgid ""
"我们通过编写 **javascript/typescript** 来测试合约。首先，在工程根目录下运行 ``npm init`` 来创建一个 "
"**npm** 项目。接下来安装依赖："
msgstr ""

#: ../../testting.rst:9 f11a434d61cc43e09b394412d231c879
msgid "安装 **scryptlib**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../testting.rst:11 7373824dfe324ba28d70147c10fc7e0c
msgid "``npm i scryptlib``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../testting.rst:15 7b3b2f50e1cc4ce6a319a295842c5002
msgid ""
"`scryptlib <https://github.com/sCrypt-Inc/scryptlib>`_ 是官方提供的用于集成以 "
"**sCrypt** 语言编写的比特币智能合约的 Javascript/TypeScript SDK。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../testting.rst:17 d08b02a8f63d4742b1145dc0d0b1cfc2
msgid "安装 **mocha** 测试框架"
msgstr ""

#: ../../testting.rst:19 03caebda8f7c43ed95838be86b292a1e
msgid "``npm i -D chai mocha``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../testting.rst:23 57bcfae7c5b44e4ea5b783ceb87c0a19
msgid "我们推荐使用 `mocha <https://mochajs.org/>`_ 测试框架来进行合约的测试，当然您可以使用其它测试框架。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../testting.rst:25 ee49673541f8418595abef927c656221
msgid "在 ``package.json`` 中配置测试命令"
msgstr ""

#: ../../testting.rst:27 7743d923ac83487397cbd89ea427d779
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"``package.json`` 文件的脚本部分中应该存在一个名为 ``single-test`` 的脚本。**sCrypt IDE** "
"用它来运行单个文件测试。通常它看起来像 \"single-test\": \"mocha\"，但您可以自定义它。"
msgstr ""
"We test the contract by writing **javascript/typescript**. We recommend "
"using the `mocha <https://mochajs.org/>`_ testing framework for contract "
"testing, of course you can use other testing frameworks. There should be "
"a script named ``single-test`` in the script section of the "
"``package.json`` file. **sCrypt IDE** uses it to run single file tests. "
"Usually it looks like \"single-test\": \"mocha\", but you can customize "
"it."

#: ../../testting.rst:53 f6f2e9424d7d494b8ee500a315cc7df9
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**sCrypt IDE** 支持在代码编辑器/资源管理器上下文菜单中运行单元测试文件。开始运行后，**sCrypt IDE** 会为你自动打开 "
"vscode 底部面板，并显示 **输出** 视图， 测试报告将输出到 **输出** 面板。"
msgstr ""
"**sCrypt IDE** supports running unit test files in the context menu of "
"the code editor/resource manager. After starting to run, **sCrypt IDE** "
"will automatically open the bottom panel of vscode for you, and display "
"the **Output** view, and the test report will be output to the **Output**"
" view."

#: ../../testting.rst:59 a7e820c7b4c845bd9cd0e3f8dc92abd4
msgid ""
"测试文件必须以 ``.scrypttest.js`` 或 ``.scrypttest.ts`` 为后缀，否则菜单中不会出现“Run sCrypt "
"Test”选项。"
msgstr ""
"The test file must be suffixed with ``.scrypttest.js`` or "
"``.scrypttest.ts``, otherwise the \"Run sCrypt Test\" option will not "
"appear in the menu."

